---
/**
 * SkipLink — keyboard-only link to jump to #main content.
 * Visually hidden until focused; required for keyboard accessibility.
 */
---
<a
  href="#main"
  class="sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:fixed focus:left-4 focus:top-4 focus:z-toast focus:rounded-md focus:bg-primary focus:px-4 focus:py-2 focus:text-sm focus:font-medium focus:text-primary-foreground focus:shadow-lg"
>
  Skip to content
</a>
